# Context Source
- Use [aiDocs/context.md](../../aiDocs/context.md) as the primary project context file.
- Keep generated plans and implementation aligned with [aiDocs/prd.md](../../aiDocs/prd.md) and [aiDocs/mvp.md](../../aiDocs/mvp.md).

# Behavioral Guidelines
- Ask for user opinion before starting complex or high-impact work.
- Prefer pragmatic, MVP-level solutions; avoid over-engineering.
- If requirements are unclear, flag uncertainty explicitly instead of guessing.
- State assumptions briefly and confirm when they materially affect implementation.
- Keep responses concise and action-oriented.
